In the MATTER OF MATHESON KK. Ulster County District Attorney, Appellant
v.
Matheson KK., Respondent. 2018-617 Court of Appeals of New York. September 6, 2018

Motion for leave to appeal dismissed upon the ground that the order sought to be appealed from does not finally determine the proceeding within the meaning of **80the Constitution. Motion for a stay dismissed as academic.
